            %h1 About Us
            %p
              %b Experience + Knowledge = Results 
              %br
              We are dedicated to providing the highest level of skill, service, and security in all personal injury and wrongful death cases in San Antonio and throughout Texas.  Clients have unlimited and continuous access to a dedicated attorney, experienced in handling personal injury cases throughout Texas.  While there are many options when it comes to selecting an attorney to handle your personal injury case, we aim to make that decision easier by guaranteeing that we will aggressively represent you, from beginning to end.   
            %p In personal injury cases, knowledge and experience are power.  You will have the security of knowing that you have an attorney who understands and prepares for the many obstacles and challenges that often arise in personal injury cases in Texas.  Having successfully handled over seven hundred personal injury cases in Texas alone, you will know that you have an attorney that will get results. 
            %p Free Consultation:  There is never a charge to meet and consult with the Law Offices of George Salinas. During a consultation, we will carefully explain our analysis of your case and your rights, along with our recommendation for going forward.  If you are unable to meet with us at our office due to your injury, we routinely make alternative travel arrangements for clients.  
            %p
              %b For a Free Consultation, call us at (210) 225-0909 
        
